Bring a large pot of water to a boil. In a large skillet saute the onion in olive oil for about 5 minutes or until slightly browned. Add the mushrooms and saute for an additional 5 minutes. Add the heavy cream and the peas; season with salt and pepper; bring to a simmer. Cook the pasta according to package directions; drain and toss with the sauce. Remove from the heat and add the Parmigiano-Reggiano cheese; toss to combine.